text: Ic Æþelnoð Christes cyrcean arcebiscop gebohte þæt land æt Godmæresham æt Sirede eorle mid twam & hundseofontigan marcan hwites seolfres be gewihte & geaf hit on minon halan life into Christes cyrcean þan hirede to bigleofan into heora beodderne for mine sawle.
& se þe þis wille awendan awende hine Crist fram heofenan rices myrhðe into helle wite.
